What you need to know:

World Athletics Under-20 Championships were programmed from July 7-12 this year but later pushed to August 17-22 next year owing to Covid-19 pandemic outbreakThe new qualification windows for the world junior event are October 1, 2019 to April 5, 2020 and December 1, 2020 to August 8, 2021Defending world champions will be offered a wild card entry, as will the winners of the 2021 Diamond League, Race Walk Challenge, Combined Events Challenge and the leading hammer performers on the Continental Tour